
Monster Traits
--------------

Image list
Animation switching interval



Play state
----------

Score
Level
Lives
Carried Items  (flags)

Walls of current room

Man Position
Man Facing Direction

List of objects (polymorphic):

Monster:
- Monster type
- Monster position
- Game-Time created  (to calc anim)

Bullet:
- Bullet position
- Bullet direction

Explosion:
- Game-Time that explosion commenced
- Explosion position

Gold / ring / key:
- Position

Potion:
- Position
- Game-Time created  (to calc anim)




